, male. 35. Dorsal view; 36. Ventral view; 37. Head, anterior view; 38. Pronotum, dorsal view; 39. Apex of elytra, posterior view. Scale line = 2.0 mm (Figs 35–36); Scale line = 0.5 mm (Figs 37–39).
